org.eclipse.swt.events
Class ShellAdapter

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.eclipse.swt.events.ShellAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener, ShellListener, org.eclipse.swt.internal.SWTEventListener
public abstract class ShellAdapter
extends Object
implements ShellListener

Unsafe: This adapter class provides default implementations for the methods described by the ShellListener interface.

Classes that wish to deal with ShellEvents can extend this class and override only the methods which they are interested in.

See Also:
ShellListener, ShellEvent
